00:27:51,369 --> 00:27:53,667
[Matt] Who is it?

478
00:27:53,772 --> 00:27:55,069
Hello?

479
00:27:57,175 --> 00:28:00,303
Director Brackett,
this is a-- Uh, come on in.

480
00:28:05,083 --> 00:28:06,482
Welcome.

481
00:28:09,020 --> 00:28:11,648
