484
00:28:17,395 --> 00:28:18,362
Okay, wh--

485
00:28:18,463 --> 00:28:20,021
- Shut up. I'm not finished.
- Okay, listen--

486
00:28:20,131 --> 00:28:21,689
- I'm shutting this operation down.
- Wait--

487
00:28:21,800 --> 00:28:23,461
- It's over.
